    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini. Temporibus domini nostri Clementi pape et universalis
                        pontificis sitque mense genuarii, indictione quintadecima, infra <rs
                            key="#Cells/hermitages">celle</rs> ... <orgName
                            key="#Houses #Canals #Monasteries #Cells/hermitages"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sancte Marie in <placeName
                                ref="#places/4179">Ponposia</placeName></orgName>. Petivi a te
                        quidem in Dei nomine domnus <persName key="#Monks"><name ref="Iohannes"
                                >Iohanni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Monks">monacho</rs> cum consensu de <persName ref="#people/1596"
                            >Mainardi</persName> ... michi presenti <persName><name
                                ref="Martinus de More">Martinus de More</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Landed_possessions">peciam terre</rs> que fuit de quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Iohannes de Ariprando">Iohannis de
                                Ariprando</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Petrus"
                                >Petrus</name></persName> et Erme... in tribus partibus, in quarta
                        vero parte ... in ipso Martinus in persona eius vice Iohannis seo filiis et
                        nepotibus vestris ... ante alter si ... filio vel filia morta fuerit, eius
                        pars danda illis qui supervixerit ... omnes res que nos abemus iure predicto
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs> in ... <rs key="#Houses"
                            >casa</rs>
                        <rs key="#Canals">canale</rs> ... ad abendum, tenendum, laborandum ...</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
